    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You point your finger, and the creature that damaged you is momentarily surrounded by hellish flames. The creature must make a Dexterity saving throw. It takes [[/damage 2d10 type=fire]] damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by [[/damage 1d10]] for each slot level above 1st.</p></div></div>",
